{"word":"G4308 - προοράω - prooráō - pro-or-ah'-o - Foresee","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προοράω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prooráō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-or-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Foresee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்னமாக அறி"},{"paragraph":"1. to see before"},{"paragraph":"2. to keep before one's eyes, to be mindful of one always"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o/3708\">G3708</a>; to <i>behold in advance</i>, that is, (active voice) to <i>notice</i> (another) <i>previously</i>, or (middle voice) to <i>keep in</i> (one&rsquo;s own) <i>view:</i> - foresee, see before.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2300/2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334/2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529/2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705/3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706/3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707/3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708/3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308/4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517/517\">G517</a>"}]}